data.meta_description: Franklin College Responsibilities Michael Brewer is a UGA Web Developer Principal and a Certified HDI Support Center Analyst. Michael's responsibilities include developing and supporting applications for intranet and internet use, creating, managing, and assisting in the migration of databases, and desktop and network support; his skills include Drupal, PHP, Javascript, Bash shell programming, PostgreSQL, MySQL, data visualization, and git.
